  "topics": [],
  "content": "The Powerhouse design systems repository (https://github.com/powerhouse-inc/design-systems) contains self-contained design system packages for three Powerhouse brands: Achra, Vetra, and the Powerhouse parent brand. There is no build step required -- all HTML files are standalone and can be opened directly in a browser or served via `npx serve`. The primary purpose of these packages is to serve as reference material for coding agents implementing designs. When building UI for a Powerhouse product, an agent references the appropriate brand's HTML/CSS files to extract colors, typography, component patterns, and layout structures. Each brand lives in its own directory (`achra/`, `vetra/`, `powerhouse/`) and follows a consistent package structure with shared conventions for color tokens, typography, and theming.",
